                                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                <p><strong>ATTENTION</strong>:</p>
                                <ol>
                                    <li>The Company does not charge any fees for deposits to the Account;</li>
                                    <li>All commissions for the transfer of funds at the expense of the Client, in accordance with clause 25 of the Agreement;</li>
                                    <li>If the funds are not credited to your investment account within the time specified above, please contact the client support service at info@tradeclan.by or by phone number +375-29-199-88-99 with a copy of the document, confirming payment to the Company.</li>
                                    <li>Deposits from third parties is not allowed, except as provided in clause 29 of the Agreement (you can download the Confirmation of the use of funds form <u>here</u>).</li>
                                </ol>
                                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                <p>To view the up-to-date list of deposit and withdrawal methods available to you, log in to your Personal Account.</p>
                                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                <h3>Withdrawal</h3>
                                <table>
