                                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                <p><strong>ATTENTION:</strong></p>
                                <ol>
                                    <li>A bank transfer fee is charged from the amount of funds sent, a commission of the receiving bank is possible, the amount of the commission of the receiving bank should be found out in your bank.</li>
                                    <li>Funds are returned strictly to the source of the deposit. The withdrawal of funds is made strictly to the credit card from which the funds were deposited.</li>
                                    <li>To view the current list of withdrawal methods, log in to your Personal Account.</li>
                                </ol>
                                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                <p>The secure WEBPAY server (www.webpay.by) establishes an encrypted connection using a secure TLS protocol and confidentially receives from the client the data of his payment card (card number, holder’s name, expiration date, and CVC/CVC2 bank card control number).</p>
                                <p>After making a payment using a bank card, it is necessary to save the received card checks (payment confirmations) for verification with an extract from the card account (in order to confirm the transactions performed in case of disputes).</p>

